<C>__{idaho }
<D>__{let's move it. everybody up and at 'em.}
<A>__{the postman comes to. he licks his dry, blood caked lips. a sudden movement startles him it's woody, shoving him a battered cup of water. it's like he's been keeping watch. the postman is surprised, a little suspicious, and very grateful as he gulps the water down.}
<C>__{the postman}
<D>__{thanks. did i win?}
